00:00:11.722 --> 00:00:12.481
First,

00:00:12.482 --> 00:00:14.761
your employer may dismiss you for 1 reason

00:00:15.080 --> 00:00:17.760
disciplinary and that even if you are on sick leave.

00:00:17.761 --> 00:00:19.841
This is the case if you have made 1 mistake

00:00:20.120 --> 00:00:20.920
before you stop.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:21.503
