00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:26.600
Even if you are on sick leave,

00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:29.400
you can have 1 economic layoff.

00:00:29.560 --> 00:00:30.052
3rd case, 

00:00:30.052 --> 00:00:31.480
your employer may dismiss you

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:34.040
